<item>
            <title>[LU-15566] sanity test 160h fails with &apos;mds1: User cl9 not registered&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15566</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity test_160h started failing on January 21, 2022 for Lustre 2.14.56.105, logs at &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b3a01514-6b50-489f-8b4f-c79da0edd637&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b3a01514-6b50-489f-8b4f-c79da0edd637&lt;/a&gt; , with the following in the suite_log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Started lustre-MDT0000
CMD: trevis-71vm9 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdd.lustre-MDT0000.changelog_users
 sanity test_160h: @@@@@@ FAIL: mds1: User cl9 not registered 
  Trace dump:
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:6389:error()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity.sh:16359:test_160h()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Another failure is at &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/0f5520f4-e4db-4a8a-9500-d77ee32b6f61&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/0f5520f4-e4db-4a8a-9500-d77ee32b6f61&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have seen this test fail during patch testing prior to the test failures listed above, starting with:&lt;br/&gt;
December 7, 2021 - Lustre 2.1.455.171 - &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/885dc3d2-bd6e-4199-8102-2c99ec8f9179&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/885dc3d2-bd6e-4199-8102-2c99ec8f9179&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We see the same error for sanity test_160f:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3c6b5a99-ddd3-4264-bcde-50255e477416&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3c6b5a99-ddd3-4264-bcde-50255e477416&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
